\c 19
\s AmaIsrayeli afika eSinayi
\p
\v 1 Ngenyanga yesithathu emva kokuphuma kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli elizweni leGibhithe, ngalelolanga bafika enkangala yeSinayi\x + 16.1. Nani 33.15.\x*.
\v 2 Sebesukile eRefidimi\x + 17.1,8.\x*, bafika enkangala yeSinayi, bamisa inkamba enkangala; uIsrayeli wamisa-ke inkamba khona phambi kwentaba\x + 3.1,12.\x*.
\v 3 UMozisi wasesenyukela kuNkulunkulu\x + 20.21. Seb. 7.38.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimemeza kuye esentabeni isithi\x + 3.4.\x*: Uzakutsho njalo kuyo indlu kaJakobe, ubatshele abantwana bakoIsrayeli \add uthi\add*:
\v 4 Lina libonile lokho engikwenze kumaGibhithe\x + Dute. 29.2.\x*, lokuthi ngalithwala phezu kwempiko zenkozi, ngaliletha kimi\x + Dute. 32.11. Isa. 40.31. Isam. 12.14.\x*.
\v 5 Ngakho-ke uba lilalela lokulalela ilizwi lami, ligcine isivumelwano sami\x + Dute. 5.2.\x*, khona lizakuba yimfuyo ekhethekileyo kimi kulazo zonke izizwe\x + Dute. 7.6; 14.2; 26.18. Hlab. 135.4. Mal. 3.17. Tit. 2.14.\x*; ngoba umhlaba wonke ungowami\x + 9.29. Dute. 10.14. Jobe 41.11. Hlab. 24.1. 50.12. 1 Kor. 10.26,28.\x*;
\v 6 njalo lizakuba ngumbuso wabapristi\x + 1 Pet. 2.5,9. Isam. 1.6. 5.10. 20.6.\x* lesizwe esingcwele kimi\x + Levi 19.2. 20.26. Dute. 7.6. 14.21. 26.19. 28.9. Isa. 62.12.\x*. Yiwo lamazwi ozawatsho kubantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 7 UMozisi wasesiza wabiza abadala babantu, wabeka phambi kwabo wonke la amazwi iN\nd kosi\nd* emlaye wona.
\v 8 Bonke abantu basebephendula kanyekanye bathi: Konke iN\nd kosi\nd* ekukhulumileyo sizakwenza\x + 24.3,7. Dute. 5.27; 26.17.\x*. UMozisi wasebuyisela amazwi abantu eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Khangela, ngizakuza kuwe eyezini elinzima\x + 19.16; 20.21; 24.15,16. Dute. 4.11. Hlab. 18.11,12; 97.2. Mat. 17.5; 16. 20.21; 24.15,16. Dute. 4.11. Hlab. 18.11,12; 97.2. Mat. 17.5.\x* ukuze abantu bezwe nxa ngikhuluma lawe\x + Dute. 4.12,36. Joha. 12.28,29.\x*, lokuthi bakholwe kuwe kuze kube nininini\x + 14.31.\x*. UMozisi wasebikela iN\nd kosi\nd* amazwi abantu.
\p
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Hamba uye ebantwini, ubangcwelise lamuhla lakusasa\x + Levi 11.44,45.\x*, bawatshe izembatho zabo\x + 19.14. Gen. 35.2. Levi 15.5.\x*,
\v 11 babe sebelungele usuku lwesithathu; ngoba ngosuku lwesithathu iN\nd kosi\nd* izakwehla phambi kwamehlo abantu bonke phezu kwentaba yeSinayi\x + 19.16,18. 34.5.\x*.
\v 12 Uzabamisela abantu umngcele inhlangothi zonke uthi: Ziqapheleni ukukhwela entabeni, lokuthinta ewatheni layo. Wonke othinta intaba uzabulawa lokubulawa\x + Heb. 12.20.\x*.
\v 13 Kakulasandla esizayithinta, kodwa sibili uzakhandwa ngamatshe loba sibili uzatshokwa; loba inyamazana loba umuntu, kakuyikuphila. Lapho uphondo lwenqama lukhala isikhathi eside bazakwenyukela entabeni\x + 19.16,19.\x*.
\p
\v 14 UMozisi wasesehla entabeni waya ebantwini, wangcwelisa abantu, njalo bahlamba izembatho zabo\x + 19.3.\x*.
\v 15 Wathi ebantwini: Lungelani usuku lwesithathu\x + 19.11.\x*; lingasondeli kowesifazana\x + 1 Sam. 21.4,5. 1 Kor. 7.5.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesithathu sekusile, kwakulemidumo lemibane\x + Hlab. 77.18. Heb. 12.18. Isam. 4.5; 8.5; 11.19.\x* leyezi elinzima phezu kwentaba\x + 19.9.\x*, lelizwi lophondo olulamandla amakhulu\x + Isam. 1.10; 4.1.\x*; kwaze kwathi bonke abantu ababesenkambeni bathuthumela\x + Heb. 12.21.\x*.
\v 17 UMozisi wasebakhupha abantu enkambeni ukuyamhlangabeza uNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 4.10.\x*; basebesima ngaphansi kwentaba.
\v 18 Intaba yonke-ke yeSinayi yathunqa intuthu\x + Isa. 6.4.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yehlela phezu kwayo ngomlilo\x + 3.2; 24.17. Dute. 4.11,36; 33.2. Hlu. 5.5.\x*; njalo intuthu yayo yenyuka njengentuthu yesithando\x + Gen. 15.17. Hlab. 144.5. Isam. 15.8.\x*; intaba yonke yasizamazama kakhulu\x + Hlab. 68.8. Heb. 12.26.\x*.
\v 19 Kwathi ilizwi lophondo liqhubeka lisiba lamandla amakhulu\x + 19.13.\x*, uMozisi wakhuluma; njalo uNkulunkulu wamphendula ngelizwi\x + Neh. 9.13. Hlab. 81.7.\x*.
\v 20 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisehlela entabeni yeSinayi, engqongeni yentaba; iN\nd kosi\nd* yambizela uMozisi engqongeni yentaba; uMozisi wenyuka-ke.
\v 21 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Yehla, ubaxwayise abantu hlezi bafohlele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ukubona\x + 3.6. 1 Sam. 6.19.\x*, njalo abanengi babo bawe.
\v 22 Labapristi labo abasondela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kabazingcwelise\x + Levi 10.3.\x* hlezi iN\nd kosi\nd* ibadumele\x + 2 Sam. 6.8.\x*.
\v 23 UMozisi wasesithi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Abantu bangenyukele entabeni yeSinayi, ngoba wena usixwayisile usithi: Misa umngcele wentaba, uyingcwelise\x + 19.12. Josh. 3.4.\x*.
\v 24 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Hamba wehle, ubuye wenyuke, wena loAroni elawe; kodwa abapristi labantu kabangafohli benyukele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, hlezi ibadumele.
\v 25 UMozisi wasesehlela ebantwini, wabatshela.
